<L>__{interior garage day}
<A>__{karl ties his books up with his strap and gets a bag from his bed and leaves.}
<L>__{exterior driveway day}
<A>__{karl is walking away as linda pulls up in her car and gets out with fast food bags.}
<C>__{linda}
<D>__{where are you goin', karl? didn't you want some chicken and things?}
