<C>__{linda}
<D>__{where'd he go? what's goin' on?}
<C>__{karl}
<D>__{he wanted to go off and play, i reckon.}
<P>__{(pause)}
<D>__{you go in there and you and that doyle eat ye dinner. you don't have to worry yourself none.}
